General.Name: FLEX LNG Ltd
General.Description: FLEX LNG Ltd., together with its subsidiaries, engages in the seaborne transportation of liquefied natural gas (LNG) worldwide. It owns and operates vessels with M-type electronically controlled gas injection LNG carriers, and vessels with generation X dual fuel propulsion systems. The company was incorporated in 2006 and is based in Hamilton, Bermuda.
